      "content": "it's just not the same though. that person had purpose. i had things i wanted to do and people who actually looked at me like i mattered. now i'm just a ghost in my own life. it feels like i'm just performing being alive while i'm actually already gone. do you think it's even possible to find meaning in a shell when the soul of it is long gone?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
